name: Phallusia
description:
Space Log 11491: "The world was rich in oxygen and vegetation similar to earth. A perfect world to inhabit, society ought to prosper well here. Then some of the men chimed in. Apparently they aren't getting a good vibe from this new world. They want to go somewhere else, I guess we will need to have a vote. Everyone else seemed overly stoked to have just found a planet where we can breathe. Surely those men will change their mind ones they try the giant vegetables that grows here in abundance."
